FBIS4-40026 "drsov113_d_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-113 Daily Report 13 Jun 1994 Regional Affairs Counterintelligence Chief Flies to Far East Counterintelligence Chief Flies to Far East LD1306102594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1007 GMT 13 Jun 94 LD1306102594 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow June 13 TASS -- Director of the Federal Counterintelligence Service (FCIS) Sergey Stepashin flew to the Far East this Monday on a working trip, during which he will visit Vladivostok, Nakhodka and the Kurile Islands. ITAR-TASS learnt at the FCIS that the director will meet population in the Far East, counterintelligence officers and will study the situation to map out measures to cut crime in the region and to realise the comprehensive crime-control programme.
